definitions.definition: The most senior rank for an academic at a university or similar institution .
A teacher or faculty member at a college or university regardless of formal rank.
One who professes something, such as a religious doctrine.
A practitioner , one who (publicly) practises or teaches an art or skill.
A pianist in a saloon , brothel , etc.
The puppeteer who performs a Punch and Judy show ; a Punchman .

main_definition: The most senior rank for an academic at a university or similar institution .
secondary_definitions: ( US , Philippines , informal ) A teacher or faculty member at a college or university regardless of formal rank.
( archaic ) One who professes something, such as a religious doctrine.
( obsolete ) A practitioner , one who (publicly) practises or teaches an art or skill.
( US , slang ) A pianist in a saloon , brothel , etc.
The puppeteer who performs a Punch and Judy show ; a Punchman .
